Upon arrival officers discovered the woman suffering from serious stab wounds to the neck, stomach and back. Her 28 year old partner was found nearby also suffering from stab wounds.

Both were taken to the Royal Preston Hospital, where the man died of his injuries.

The woman has since been transferred to Royal Blackburn Hospital where she remains in a critical condition.

